# REVOLUTION TRADING PROS - CLOUDFLARE PAGES HEADERS
# âš¡ LIGHTNING STACK - Performance & Security Headers
#
# These headers are automatically applied by Cloudflare Pages.
# @see https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
